    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power through its individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains composed with a functional variable M differential lock ensuring traction through the apex. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including a Vanos system refresh and a structural inspection of the rear subframe mounts to ensure torsional rigidity. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with enthusiast use, the powertrain remains potent and the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering provides the communicative feedback these M-cars are known for. Riding on staggered Style 67 alloys, this M3 is a turn-key driver's car with its performance envelope fully intact.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
