    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior paint still holds a deep, glassy shine, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from standard garage parking\u2014nothing that detracts from its overall presence. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seats are firm and comfortable, showing only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All technology features, including the navigation system and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in great shape; it has a documented service history with recent oil and filter changes, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. The engine runs quietly, and the transmission shifts smoothly under all driving conditions. This is a dependable, honest vehicle that is ready to be driven home today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
